\q1
\v 7 ThenВҰ378864 Efrayim \add (EphraimВҰ378866, referring to Israel)\add* will be like a warriorВҰ378865,
\q1 and their hearts will rejoice as withВҰ378877 wine;
\q1 Their childrenВҰ378872 will seeВҰ378873 and rejoice.
\q1 вүҲTheir hearts will rejoice inВҰ378877 me!
\b
\q1
\v 8 I'll whistleВҰ378879 \add to call\add* them and gatherВҰ378881 them,
\q1 becauseВҰ378882 I'll rescue them,
\q1 and they'll become as numerousВҰ378884 as they were previously.
