\q1
\v 11 \add @Yahweh\add* will \add вүҲlead them through their sufferings\add*.
\q1 \add вүҲHe\add* will strikeВҰ378916 the wavesВҰ378918 of that sea
\q1 вүҲand will dry up all the depthsВҰ378921 of the Nile.
